{"id": "hard_analysis_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "证明：若函数 f(x) 在 [0,1] 上连续，在 (0,1) 内可导，且 f(0)=0, f(1)=1，则存在 ξ∈(0,1) 使得 f'(ξ)=2ξ。", "answer": "令 g(x)=f(x)-x²，则 g(0)=0, g(1)=0。由罗尔定理，存在 ξ∈(0,1) 使 g'(ξ)=0，即 f'(ξ)=2ξ。"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "计算极限：lim_{x→0} (e^x - 1 - x - x²/2) / x³", "answer": "使用泰勒展开：e^x = 1 + x + x²/2 + x³/6 + O(x⁴)，代入得极限 = 1/6。"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "判断级数 ∑_{n=1}^{∞} (n!)/(n^n) 的收敛性。", "answer": "比值判别法：lim a_{n+1}/a_n = lim 1/(1+1/n)^n = 1/e < 1，故收敛。"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_4", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "计算二重积分 ∬_D sin(x+y) dxdy，D: x=0,y=0,x+y=π 围成的三角形。", "answer": "= ∫_0^π ∫_0^{π-x} sin(x+y) dy dx = ∫_0^π (1+cos x) dx = π。"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_5", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "求幂级数 ∑_{n=1}^{∞} n²x^n 的收敛域及和函数。", "answer": "收敛域 (-1,1)。∑n²x^n = x(1+x)/(1-x)³。"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_6", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "证明：在 R² 中，如果开集族 {U_i}_{i∈I} 覆盖了紧集 K，则存在有限子覆盖。", "answer": "紧集定义：K 的每个开覆盖都有有限子覆盖。此即紧集的定义，无需证明。若需从R²的Heine-Borel定理出发：K有界闭→K的任意开覆盖有有限子覆盖。"}
{"id": "hard_calc_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Calculus", "question": "求曲线 y = x³ - 3x² + 2x 在点 (1,0) 处的切线与法线方程。", "answer": "y' = 3x²-6x+2, x=1时y'=-1。切线: y=-x+1, 法线: y=x-1。"}
{"id": "hard_calc_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Calculus", "question": "求函数 f(x)=x⁴-4x³+6x²-4x+1 的极值点和拐点。f(x)=(x-1)⁴ 是否有帮助？", "answer": "f(x)=(x-1)⁴, x=1是最小值点（非拐点，f''(1)=0但f'在1两侧不变号）。"}
{"id": "hard_calc_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Calculus", "question": "求曲线 y = x·ln x 在 x=1 处的曲率。", "answer": "y' = ln x + 1, y'' = 1/x。在 x=1: y'=1, y''=1。曲率 K = |y''|/(1+y'²)^(3/2) = 1/(2√2) = √2/4。"}
{"id": "hard_calc_4", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Calculus", "question": "求广义积分 ∫_1^{∞} 1/(x²+1) dx", "answer": "∫ 1/(1+x²)dx = arctan x。∫_1^{∞} = π/2 - π/4 = π/4。"}
{"id": "hard_la_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Linear Algebra", "question": "设 A 是 n 阶实对称矩阵，证明：A 正定当且仅当所有顺序主子式 > 0。", "answer": "这是Sylvester准则。必要性：A=PᵀP⇒主子式>0。充分性：归纳法。"}
{"id": "hard_la_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Linear Algebra", "question": "求所有满足 A² = I 的 2×2 实矩阵 A（对合矩阵）。", "answer": "设A=[[a,b],[c,d]]，由A²=I得：①A=±I ②A=[[1,0],[c,-1]] ③A=[[-1,0],[c,1]] ④A=[[a,b],[(1-a²)/b,-a]], b≠0"}
{"id": "hard_la_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Linear Algebra", "question": "设 V 为次数≤3的多项式空间，T:V→V, T(f)=f'+f(0)。求T的特征值和特征向量。", "answer": "在基{1,x,x²,x³}下T的矩阵[[1,0,0,0],[1,0,0,0],[0,2,0,0],[0,0,3,0]]。特征值λ=1（重数1）和λ=0（重数3）。"}
{"id": "hard_nt_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "求所有正整数解 (x,y) 满足 x² - y² = 2024。", "answer": "x²-y²=(x-y)(x+y)=2024=2³×11×23。解得：(x,y)=(507,505),(255,251),(69,59),(57,43),(39,17),(33,5)"}
{"id": "hard_nt_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "证明：存在无穷多个素数 p ≡ 3 (mod 4)。", "answer": "反证法。设有限个p₁...pₖ，构造N=4p₁...pₖ-1。N≡3(mod4)故有素因子q≡3(mod4)，但q不是任一pᵢ，矛盾。"}
{"id": "hard_nt_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "求 2024! 末尾有多少个连续的零？", "answer": "由因子5的个数决定：⌊2024/5⌋+⌊2024/25⌋+⌊2024/125⌋+⌊2024/625⌋ = 404+80+16+3 = 503。"}
{"id": "hard_nt_4", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "证明 n⁵ - n 能被 30 整除（对任意正整数 n）。", "answer": "n⁵-n=n(n-1)(n+1)(n²+1)。连续三数含2和3的因子。若n≡0,±1(mod5)则被5整除；若n≡±2(mod5)则n²+1被5整除。故被30整除。"}
{"id": "hard_combo_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Combinatorics", "question": "从1到100中随机选3个不同数，求构成等差数列的概率。", "answer": "总C(100,3)=161700。等差数列总数=2∑_{d=1}^{49}(100-2d)=4900。概率=4900/161700=49/1617≈3.03%"}
{"id": "hard_combo_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Combinatorics", "question": "证明：正整数n拆分为互不相同正整数之和的方法数，等于拆分为奇数之和的方法数。（用生成函数）", "answer": "互不相同分割GF:∏(1+q^k)。奇数分割GF:∏1/(1-q^{2k-1})。由(1+q^k)=(1-q^{2k})/(1-q^k)得一式=∏1/(1-q^{2k-1})。"}
{"id": "hard_combo_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Combinatorics", "question": "10个人围圆桌就座，如果A和B不能相邻，有多少种坐法？", "answer": "总圆排列(10-1)!=9!。A和B相邻视作一人：(9-1)!×2=8!×2。答案=9!-8!×2=8!×(9-2)=7×8! = 282240。"}
{"id": "hard_ineq_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Inequality", "question": "已知 a,b,c>0 且 a+b+c=1，证明：a/(b+c)+b/(c+a)+c/(a+b) ≥ 3/2。", "answer": "由柯西：∑a/(b+c)·∑a(b+c) ≥ 1，∑a(b+c)=2∑ab ≤ 2/3。故原式 ≥ 3/2。"}
{"id": "hard_ineq_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Inequality", "question": "证明：对任意正实数x,y,z，有x/(y+z)+y/(z+x)+z/(x+y) ≥ 3/2。（Nesbitt不等式）", "answer": "令S=x+y+z，则原式=∑S/(S-x)-3。由柯西∑S/(S-x)≥9/(∑(S-x)/S)=9/2。故原式≥3/2。"}
{"id": "hard_geo_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Geometry", "question": "等边三角形内一点P到三边距离分别为2,3,4，求边长。", "answer": "距离和=高，2+3+4=9=√3/2·a，a=18/√3=6√3。"}
{"id": "hard_geo_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Geometry", "question": "四面体ABCD中AB=CD=5, AC=BD=6, AD=BC=7，求体积。", "answer": "对棱相等→可置入长方体。设三边x,y,z：x²+y²=25, x²+z²=36, y²+z²=49。解得x²=6,y²=19,z²=30。V=√(6×19×30)/3=2√95。"}
{"id": "hard_prob_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Probability", "question": "设X~N(0,1)，求 E[X²e^X]。", "answer": "= e^{1/2}·E[(Y+1)²] 其中Y~N(0,1) = e^{1/2}·(1+1) = 2√e。"}
{"id": "hard_prob_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Probability", "question": "在长度为1的线段上随机取两点，求距离 > 1/2 的概率。", "answer": "单位正方形中满足|x-y|>1/2的面积为1/4，概率=1/4。"}
{"id": "hard_ode_1", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Differential Equations", "question": "求解 y''+4y=sin(2x), y(0)=0, y'(0)=1", "answer": "yh=C₁cos2x+C₂sin2x, yp=-(x/4)cos2x。y=(5/8)sin2x-(x/4)cos2x。"}
{"id": "hard_ode_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Differential Equations", "question": "求 (x²+1)y'+2xy=4x² 的通解。", "answer": "积分因子 μ=x²+1。通解 y=(4x³/3+C)/(x²+1)。"}
